    {
      "id": "9983dc72_bdd89cf6",
      "file_path": "Dockerfiles/aai-common/Dockerfile.alpine",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 27,
      "message": "In the recent onap discuss, they mentioned the security vulnerability to using the shadow package.\n\nhttps://alpinelinux.org/posts/Docker-image-vulnerability-CVE-2019-5021.html\n\nIt seems that adding the following should address that concern from the article. \n\n# make sure root login is disabled\nsed -i -e 's/^root::/root:!:/' /etc/shadow",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 75,
        "name": "Venkata Harish Kajur",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "vk250x@att.com",
        "username": "vk250x"
      },
      "updated": "2019-05-12 18:34:10.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "29182d80_4a49db82",
      "file_path": "Dockerfiles/aai-common/Dockerfile.alpine",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 28,
      "message": "I don't think we need the util-linux and vim packages. Its not necessary as basic vi comes with the docker image. It shaves off another 30 MB of the common image.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 75,
        "name": "Venkata Harish Kajur",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "vk250x@att.com",
        "username": "vk250x"
      },
      "updated": "2019-05-12 18:34:10.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "a4b4a2b3_21461db9",
      "file_path": "Dockerfiles/aai-common/Dockerfile.alpine",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 27,
      "message": "According to the article mentioned:\n\"... The issue was fixed in the following Docker image releases (7 March 2019):\nv3.9.2 ...\"\n\nVersion of Alpine used in aai-common:\n# cat /etc/os-release \n...\nVERSION_ID=3.9.3\n...\n\nalso checking of /etc/shadow shows that:\n# cat /etc/shadow\nroot:!::0:::::\n\nI believe we're safe here.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5040,
        "name": "Dmitrii Puzikov",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "d.puzikov2@partner.samsung.com",
        "username": "dpuzikov"
      },
      "updated": "2019-05-13 09:48:44.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "9983dc72_bdd89cf6",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
